titleInfo.title: United States of America v. Schilke et al (DO NOT FILE DOCUMENTS IN CASE PER FILING #50)
titleInfo.subTitle: JUDGMENT AND DECREE OF FORECLOSURE AND ORDER OF SALE BY CONSENT in the amount of $133,455.38, plus accrued interest in the amount of $23,579.12, together with interest accruing at the rate of $18.2816 per day from July 21, 2006, until the date of entry of this decree, together with interest at the legal rate thereafter, plus the costs of this action. Interest will accrue on said sums from and after the date of entry of this decree at the legal rate of 5.07 percent computed daily and compounded annually until paid in full; setting priority of liens and directing sale of premises. Ordered by Judge Lyle E. Strom. (CJP) Modified on 8/30/2006 to remove copies mailed (CJP).
